LITTLE ROCK, Ark. (KTHV) – Another week is in the books for high school football in Arkansas. We had some exciting games and a few surprises, too. 
Check out some of the highlights: 
Conway Christian 20, England 27 England remains undefeated with win over Conway Christian KTHV 
Greenwood 56, Conway 19 Greenwood wins big at Conway KTHV 
Russellville 24, LR Catholic 31 LR Catholic gets comeback win over Russellville KTHV 
Jonesboro 64, NLR 70 NLR wins shootout over Jonesboro 70-64 KTHV 
Mountain home 7, LR Central 41 LR Central wins big over Mountain Home 41-7 KTHV 
Beebe 13, Pulaski Academy 49 Pulaski Academy wins big over Beebe KTHV 
Jacksonville 14, Sylvan Hills 29 Bears overcome penalties to beat Jacksonville KTHV 
Greenbrier 42, Maumelle 40 Greenbrier hangs on to beat Maumelle KTHV 
Vilonia 23, LR Christian 40 LR Christian gets home win over Vilonia KTHV
